data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET- BUYERS REMORSE!   Welcome to your serene oasis nestled in the heart of Lakeland.  This exquisite one-story ranch-style home offers an idyllic blend of privacy, comfort and the perfect opportunity for relaxed living. As you step inside you'll be greeted by an inviting and spacious living area, seamlessly connecting to the cozy wood-burning fireplace that sets the tone for cozy evenings. The layout effortlessly transitions to a well-appointed kitchen, boasting modern stainless steel Samsung appliances updated in 2020, ample counter space, and a charming dining area perfect for hosting gatherings and entertaining on the lanai. The split floor plan offers the large owners suite privacy and a separate access to the screened in lanai and outdoor pool.  The additional bedrooms offer versatility for guest rooms, home offices, or creative spaces to suit your lifestyle. All exterior doors were replaced with the current seller along with the pool pump and filter.   Located in a NO HOA or NO CDD community, this home offers convenient access to US 98 and toll roads with nearby amenities, schools, and recreational opportunities. Washer and Dryer does not convey with the property.  Sellers concession of $5K towards full offer.
